<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-2"><a href="./Capabilities#Molecular_Electronic_Structure"><span class="tocnumber">1.1</span> <span class="toctext">Molecular Electronic Structure</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-3"><a href="./Capabilities#Quantum_Mechanics.2FMolecular_Mechanics_.28QM.2FMM.29"><span class="tocnumber">1.2</span> <span class="toctext">Quantum Mechanics/Molecular Mechanics (QM/MM)</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-4"><a href="./Capabilities#Pseudopotential_Plane-Wave_Electronic_Structure"><span class="tocnumber">1.3</span> <span class="toctext">Pseudopotential Plane-Wave Electronic Structure</span></a></li>
